text:
Have a sprain foot and in pain. Came here hoping it can get some relieve. Dr did a light massage and cracking some shoulders and neck bone. 10 mins pay $50 and pain is still there without any difference.
Costly and non effective.

Whenever I have tight neck, back pain, numbness (this time is left hand and legs) I always seek treatment here. I must say they are really good and professional, affordable and best part is very effective! I wish they stay forever and I hope everyone who wants alternative treatment in a natural affordable way, this place is must go. They help me and my husband solve stiff neck, stiff shoulder or whatever pain we have due to bad body posture and lifestyle. HIGHLY RECOMMENDED!  Thank you both Mr Ho!!! You guys rock!!

Seriously a best place to treat ur painful nerves! Be it sprains, stiffness, body postures or what not Mr Ho will definitely cure it all.believe me ..n they dun cheat on ur money infact he doesn't want u to come bk he believes to cure the person truly at a go unless yes its an pain that u ve been living long than definitely 2 to 3 visit I reckon. Its a must visit place at least once a mth to keep a healthy n painless body.kufo to father n son .tq so much .

Went there three times. Not disappointing every time.
After each session, I'm able to walk better.
The father helped to adjust my back and loosen my tight muscles.
Fantastic service at great price.
If you are suffering from pain/discomfort on your neck or shoulder for days, highly recommended to this TCM. You will definitely feel the difference immediately. Thumbs up!
